{"tid":287597,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"獨遊馬拉","createTime":"2017-06-17T14:01:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T13:58:42.000Z","uid":115656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1c0e9174054fcc6e8869d75a9899501114998bb5","tid":287597,"uid":115656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T14:01:59.000Z","msg":"因為對獨自喺外地生活嘅嚮往，小妹申請喺馬拉嘅公司，從六月中到七月中喺檳城工作。同屋企人喺吉隆坡去完旅行，我就自己搭巴士由吉隆坡一個不知名巴士站去檳城啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解係不知名？因為我本來打算KL sentral中央車站搭transportation巴士去檳城，因為車站有網上訂票，車站又比較新、大、靚，起碼車次係上網check到，感覺較有保障，所以就算離我當時住嘅酒店遠，我都選擇Call Grabcar去KL sentral。<br />\n<br />\n殊不知，Grabcar grab到伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n先係司機停錯位，我等極等唔到；上到車同司機傾偈，就嚟料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />司機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />在下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Where are you from? China?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> No, Hong Kong<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Hong Kong is China.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />In your country, no marry no fuck? no marry fuck, OK?<br />\n(已經驚驚地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做咩問到咁，我開始用google map check my location，然後同朋友保持聯繫)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> You? I will pay one thousand<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n後尾司機話有個車站比KL sentral近，又有檳城車，結果就車咗我去嗰個車站(因為司機係馬拉人，佢嘅英文其實我唔太聽得明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)直到呢刻，我都唔知究竟我由咩車站上車。<br />\n<br />\n由於太驚，我一落車就衝走，拿拿林買咗張車票，價值MY50。成個車站聊聊可數兩個華人，係一對當地華人情侶，我即刻痴住佢地，佢地同我講：你俾人呃啦，我地買MY40<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢一刻我就開始懷疑未來呢個月要點過呀，人生路不熟，終於知道怕，嗚呀！"},{"pid":"84a067bcbcffa0d8a0eb44076589cc5d44274738","tid":287597,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T14:05:09.000Z","msg":"Good luck"},{"pid":"7d0ab337beed8f677b6db0a4c222b2a5075fe6b6","tid":287597,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T14:33:00.000Z","msg":"檳城好多華人，廣東話嘅有，唔知廣東或福建邊度嘅話又有，唔洗擔心。"},{"pid":"2617c031e382fff8f7cf942ddd91d738a66c04e6","tid":287597,"uid":123414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T15:19:43.000Z","msg":"我七月頭就一個去檳城自由行, 希望好玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c99ee478085ec4c90a99bebf2400f87a89eae61","tid":287597,"uid":43521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T15:36:03.000Z","msg":"檳城算係馬拉最安全既地方，不過都要注意安全<br />\n係交通唔方便，又塞車巴士又唔準時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，"},{"pid":"df2d6614a21618e6382385d2d8121b20f71e7255","tid":287597,"uid":30785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T13:40:32.000Z","msg":"黎緊呢個星期出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留名"},{"pid":"edfa4fc7929a1b39101c73f56cc4abffc8c432b1","tid":287597,"uid":123414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T13:58:42.000Z","msg":"請問有無人知光大D找換店週日開唔開工架? 或者會唔會早關門?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}